data.description: This Colonial boasts an abundance of natural light, accentuating its inviting ambiance from the moment you step inside. This home showcases recent upgrades including a new roof in 2019 and a brand-new water tank installed in 2024, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. As you explore the first floor, you'll appreciate the sleek allure of new vinyl flooring, offering both durability and style.  Upstairs, hardwood floors exude timeless elegance, adding warmth and character to every room. Embrace the beauty of the outdoors within the comfort of your fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying peaceful moments of relaxation.  Inside, spacious bedrooms provide ample retreat space, while a generously sized family room sets the stage for countless memorable gatherings.  ***Includes adjacent lot Parcel # 53012030100000
